<br>
It was a rather well known fact before PoP went live that this expansion was mainly aimed at the end game raiding type of players.  SoE themselves even admitted that while the game would contain content for the casual player it was focused around the concept of raiding the planes.<br>
<br>
There are players upon Tunare that have managed to make it into CoD, HoH and Tactics without killing any of the flagged mobs.  It may not be easy but then it should be just as difficult and challenging as actually killing the required mobs.<br>
